<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 12:12:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>德国警方在全国范围内进行了十几次突击行动，镇压哈马斯支持者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-23/ty-article/germany-cracks-down-on-hamas-supporters-in-over-a-dozen-police-raids-countrywide/0000018b-fbb5-dafe-a18f-fbf5c8e80000</link><description>在联邦禁止哈马斯和萨米敦之后，德国警方已开始执行禁令并进一步调查这些组织的存在。德国执法部长表示，我们已发出明确信号，即我们不会容忍任何美化哈马斯针对以色列的野蛮恐怖行为</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 11:42:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-23/ty-article/germany-cracks-down-on-hamas-supporters-in-over-a-dozen-police-raids-countrywide/0000018b-fbb5-dafe-a18f-fbf5c8e80000</guid></item><item><title>也门胡塞武装：他们对以色列的红海贸易构成什么威胁？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/yemens-houthis-what-threat-do-they-pose-to-israels-red-sea-trade/0000018b-fbd4-d330-a9bb-ffd64be20000</link><description>如果胡塞武装不仅开始攻击以色列人拥有的船只，而且还攻击往返以色列的船只，会发生什么？ “海洋世界是敏感的，不稳定的安全环境会产生立竿见影的影响”</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 11:30:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/yemens-houthis-what-threat-do-they-pose-to-israels-red-sea-trade/0000018b-fbd4-d330-a9bb-ffd64be20000</guid></item><item><title>拜登的困境：加沙四天休战结束后美国想要什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/bidens-dilemma-what-does-u-s-want-when-four-day-truce-ends-in-gaza/0000018b-fb78-dafe-a18f-fb799fec0000</link><description>停火期满后，美国人是否支持以色列和哈马斯恢复战争？达到什么政治目的？如果不是，这与美国一再声明哈马斯不能在战后第二天继续掌权有何相容？</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 11:16:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/bidens-dilemma-what-does-u-s-want-when-four-day-truce-ends-in-gaza/0000018b-fb78-dafe-a18f-fb799fec0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列：周五之前不会释放人质；卡塔尔表示即将宣布停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-no-hostage-release-before-friday-qatar-says-cease-fire-announcement-imminent/0000018b-fb3e-dafe-a18f-fb7f285b0000</link><description>一位熟悉谈判的以色列消息人士告诉《国土报》，协议执行的延迟并不是谈判破裂的结果，而是行政问题造成的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 10:16:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/israel-no-hostage-release-before-friday-qatar-says-cease-fire-announcement-imminent/0000018b-fb3e-dafe-a18f-fb7f285b0000</guid></item><item><title>“老人带着孩子，离开他们来吧”：与以色列士兵沿着加沙的逃生路线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/old-man-with-kids-leave-them-and-come-with-israels-soldiers-along-gazas-escape-route/0000018b-f663-d117-abcf-f7efe85a0000</link><description>数百名流离失所的巴勒斯坦人周日在废墟和爆炸声中向加沙南部游行。扩音器里时不时地传来以色列国防军播音员的声音，要求其中一人退出队列。当居民不服从命令时，以色列国防军士兵向空中开枪。 《国土报》参加了记者参观“人道主义走廊”的活动</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 09:25:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/old-man-with-kids-leave-them-and-come-with-israels-soldiers-along-gazas-escape-route/0000018b-f663-d117-abcf-f7efe85a0000</guid></item><item><title>人质协议不会带来胜利，因为以色列未来几天将面临紧张局势</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-will-yield-no-victory-laps-as-israel-faces-nerve-racking-days-ahead/0000018b-f8f5-dafe-a18f-fbf50bdd0000</link><description>以色列的风险评估和犹豫主要围绕停火问题。哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔正在争取时间，他承诺寻找并解救更多被加沙其他派系绑架的以色列人</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 06:50:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/hostage-deal-will-yield-no-victory-laps-as-israel-faces-nerve-racking-days-ahead/0000018b-f8f5-dafe-a18f-fbf50bdd0000</guid></item><item><title>真主党声称对黎巴嫩自战争开始以来最严重的火箭弹袭击负责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-live/israel-no-hostage-release-before-friday-gaza-cease-fire-also-put-on-hold/0000018b-fa3e-dafe-a18f-fb7f7d420000</link><description>以色列国家安全顾问表示，周五之前不会释放人质 ■ 以色列官员称，执行延迟是由于“正在解决”的行政事务，敦促“无需担心” ■ 加沙 Al-Shifa 医院院长在人道主义走廊被捕前往加沙地带南部 ■ 据报道，以色列在黎巴嫩发动空袭，真主党高级政客的儿子被杀 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵丧生，236 名人质在加沙地带被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：加沙有 14,128 人死亡</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 03:42:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-live/israel-no-hostage-release-before-friday-gaza-cease-fire-also-put-on-hold/0000018b-fa3e-dafe-a18f-fb7f7d420000</guid></item><item><title>以色列医院面临的棘手创伤问题：如何治疗从哈马斯囚禁中释放的婴儿？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/tough-trauma-questions-for-israeli-hospitals-how-do-you-treat-babies-who-dont-speak-yet/0000018b-f8f4-dafe-a18f-fbf548bd0000</link><description>以色列已就接收被扣为人质的儿童制定了建议。该文件包括对与儿童进行初次接触的安保人员的说明：要求他们介绍自己的姓名，并重点询问有关他们身体状况的问题</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 03:34:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/tough-trauma-questions-for-israeli-hospitals-how-do-you-treat-babies-who-dont-speak-yet/0000018b-f8f4-dafe-a18f-fbf548bd0000</guid></item><item><title>反伊斯兰民粹主义者威尔德斯将在荷兰取得巨大胜利，震惊欧洲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/anti-islam-populist-wilders-heading-for-a-massive-win-in-netherlands-in-a-shock-for-europe/0000018b-f995-d330-a9bb-ffd79f860000</link><description>维尔德斯的选举计划包括呼吁对荷兰退出欧盟进行公投、完全停止接受寻求庇护者以及在荷兰边境阻止移民。它还主张荷兰“去伊斯兰化”。匈牙利总统欧尔班很快表示祝贺</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 00:40:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/anti-islam-populist-wilders-heading-for-a-massive-win-in-netherlands-in-a-shock-for-europe/0000018b-f995-d330-a9bb-ffd79f860000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔发放枪支许可证时，以色列福利官员发出家庭暴力警告</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officials-sound-domestic-violence-warning-as-ben-gvir-dishes-out-gun-permits/0000018b-f8f6-d473-affb-f9fe0a630000</link><description>福利部对国家安全部长允许越来越多的以色列人携带武器的政策表示担忧，这与民间社会和女权主义团体已经表达的担忧相呼应</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 00:28:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/israeli-officials-sound-domestic-violence-warning-as-ben-gvir-dishes-out-gun-permits/0000018b-f8f6-d473-affb-f9fe0a630000</guid></item><item><title>太少、太慢：专家警告说，以色列和哈马斯的暂停对加沙来说是“人道主义创可贴”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/too-little-too-slow-experts-say-israel-hamas-pause-is-humanitarian-band-aid-for-gaza/0000018b-f973-d783-a3df-f97bb4260000</link><description>由于缺乏执行机制和实地独立观察员的存在，以色列与哈马斯的停战协议尤其脆弱。当前的关键问题之一是援助物资可以通过拉法进入的规定，拉法是为行人和小型车辆通行而设计的</description><pubDate>Thu, 23 Nov 2023 00:05:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article/.premium/too-little-too-slow-experts-say-israel-hamas-pause-is-humanitarian-band-aid-for-gaza/0000018b-f973-d783-a3df-f97bb4260000</guid></item><item><title>走向伪民主之路：以色列急于取悦警察及其危险的逮捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/israels-eager-to-please-police-and-its-dangerous-arrests/0000018b-f8f6-d473-affb-f9fe80cb0000</link><description>免于任意逮捕的自由标志着真正的、寻求自由的民主国家和“伪民主国家”之间的界限。不能依赖本·格维尔阴影下的警察给予言论自由应有的重视</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 23:28:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/israels-eager-to-please-police-and-its-dangerous-arrests/0000018b-f8f6-d473-affb-f9fe80cb0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯屠杀后戈兰高地德鲁兹加速“以色列化”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/since-the-hamas-massacre-golan-druze-trending-toward-israelization/0000018b-f88b-d473-affb-f9eb75ea0000</link><description>一位当地领导人在谈及 10 月 7 日哈马斯大屠杀时表示，“我们和平安全地生活在这里，突然间所有红线都被跨越了”。当以军完成对当地警卫中队的训练后，态度的转变成为当地的事实</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 23:19:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-23/ty-article-magazine/.premium/since-the-hamas-massacre-golan-druze-trending-toward-israelization/0000018b-f88b-d473-affb-f9eb75ea0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡想要一场永无休止的战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-wants-a-never-ending-war/0000018b-f894-d473-affb-f9fc179a0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 22:40:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-wants-a-never-ending-war/0000018b-f894-d473-affb-f9fc179a0000</guid></item><item><title>乔拉·艾兰的可怕的加沙提议是显而易见的邪恶</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/giora-eilands-monstrous-gaza-proposal-is-evil-in-plain-sight/0000018b-f84b-d473-affb-f9eb09af0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 22:15:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-23/ty-article-opinion/.premium/giora-eilands-monstrous-gaza-proposal-is-evil-in-plain-sight/0000018b-f84b-d473-affb-f9eb09af0000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-22/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-f8ea-dafe-a18f-fbebd49b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 21:27:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-22/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-f8ea-dafe-a18f-fbebd49b0000</guid></item><item><title>新民意调查显示，四分之三的巴勒斯坦人支持哈马斯 10 月 7 日的袭击。为什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/three-quarters-of-palestinians-support-hamas-attack-on-october-7-says-new-poll-why/0000018b-f841-d473-affb-f9e9eeef0000</link><description>两项新的民意调查提供了对战时巴勒斯坦人心态的深入了解。为了理解研究结果，我们必须考虑受访者的概念世界，他们生活在一个从未自由且总是处于战争状态的社会中</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 19:30:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/three-quarters-of-palestinians-support-hamas-attack-on-october-7-says-new-poll-why/0000018b-f841-d473-affb-f9e9eeef0000</guid></item><item><title>“比比担心释放人质的政治结果”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/my-estimate-is-that-bibis-afraid-of-the-political-result-of-releasing-the-hostages/0000018b-f7e3-d330-a9bb-fff70c460000</link><description>摩萨德行动前负责人兼囚犯交换特使哈盖·哈达斯认为他知道哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔策划 10 月 7 日大屠杀的原因</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 17:13:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/my-estimate-is-that-bibis-afraid-of-the-political-result-of-releasing-the-hostages/0000018b-f7e3-d330-a9bb-fff70c460000</guid></item><item><title>四天暂停结束后，美国希望以色列在加沙军事行动中更加克制</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/u-s-hoping-israel-uses-more-restraint-in-gaza-military-operations-after-four-day-pause/0000018b-f767-dafe-a18f-f76758480000</link><description>美国国务院谴责以色列本周早些时候对加沙联合国法库拉学校的袭击。尽管拜登总统继续支持以色列消灭哈马斯的目标，但官员们对加沙南部的行动感到担忧</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 16:43:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-22/ty-article/.premium/u-s-hoping-israel-uses-more-restraint-in-gaza-military-operations-after-four-day-pause/0000018b-f767-dafe-a18f-f76758480000</guid></item><item><title>拜登如何敲定以色列与哈马斯人质协议的幕后花絮</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/behind-the-scenes-on-how-biden-hammered-out-the-israel-hamas-hostage-deal/0000018b-f757-d7a8-a9cf-f77f58560000</link><description>自从 10 月 7 日哈马斯从以色列绑架了约 240 人以来，美国、卡塔尔和埃及一直在积极努力达成一项协议，以确保他们获释。一名美国官员透露如何最终达成在未来几天内释放 50 名人质的协议</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Nov 2023 15:46:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/behind-the-scenes-on-how-biden-hammered-out-the-israel-hamas-hostage-deal/0000018b-f757-d7a8-a9cf-f77f58560000</guid></item></channel></rss>